rth cts lk  gnt br mgnt wth  mgntc nrth pl nd  mgntc sth pl. Lk ny mgnt, t fllws th bsc rl tht ppst pls ttrct nd lk pls rpl.
S f y hv  cmpss ndl (whch s  smll mgnt):
	•	Th nrth nd f th cmpss ndl s ttrctd t rth's mgntc sth pl
	•	Th sth nd f th cmpss ndl s ttrctd t rth's mgntc nrth pl
