S nrth rpls

:ctlly, lt m clrfy ths - t dpnds n wht y mn by "nrth rpls."
Nrth rpls nrth - tht's crrct! Lk mgntc pls rpl ch thr.
Bt hr's whr t gts  bt cnfsng wth rth's mgntsm:
	•	Th nrth nd f  cmpss ndl s rplld by thr nrth pls
	•	Hwvr, th nrth nd f  cmpss ndl s ttrctd t wht w cll "mgntc nrth" n rth
	•	Ths hppns bcs rth's "mgntc nrth pl" s ctlly  mgntc sth pl n trms f ts plrty
S t b prcs:
	•	Lk pls rpl: Nrth rpls nrth, sth rpls sth
	•	ppst pls ttrct: Nrth ttrcts sth, sth ttrcts nrth
Th cnfsng prt s jst th nmng cnvntn - wht w cll rth's "mgntc nrth pl" (whr cmpss ndls pnt) s ctlly th sth pl f rth's mgntc fld.
Ds tht hlp clrfy th psh/pll rltnshp? Th fndmntl rl s lwys: lk rpls lk, ppsts ttrct.

