Gt t. S r Nrth Pl pshs nd r Sth Pl plls rght?
: cn s why y mght thnk tht, bt t's nt qt rght t sy n pl nly pshs nd th thr nly plls. Bth pls cn psh ND pll dpndng n wht thy'r ntrctng wth:
rth's Nrth Pl (mgntc sth plrty):
	•	Plls th nrth nd f cmpss ndls (ppst pls ttrct)
	•	Pshs wy ny thr mgntc sth pls (lk pls rpl)
rth's Sth Pl (mgntc nrth plrty):
	•	Plls th sth nd f cmpss ndls (ppst pls ttrct)
	•	Pshs wy ny thr mgntc nrth pls (lk pls rpl)
S ch pl bth pshs nd plls - t ll dpnds n wht knd f mgntc pl t's ntrctng wth. Th ky rl s lwys:
	•	ppst pls ttrct (pll twrd ch thr)
	•	Lk pls rpl (psh wy frm ch thr)
Thnk f t ths wy: vry mgnt s lwys dng bth pshng nd pllng smltnsly, jst n dffrnt drctns dpndng n wht's rnd t.
Ds tht mk th rltnshp clrr?

sr:
Th fld cms t f th nrth nd crvs rnd t th sth crrct?

:ctlly, t's th ppst! Mgntc fld lns cm t f th sth pl nd crv rnd t ntr th nrth pl.
Hr's th cnvntn:
	•	Mgntc fld lns xt frm th sth pl
	•	Mgntc fld lns ntr nt th nrth pl
Fr rth spcfclly:
	•	Fld lns cm t f th Sth Pl (ntrctc rgn)
	•	Thy crv thrgh spc rnd th plnt
	•	Thy ntr bck nt th Nrth Pl (rctc rgn)
Ths mght sm cntrnttv t frst, bt t's th stndrd cnvntn n physcs. Y cn thnk f th fld lns s shwng th pth tht  ln nrth pl wld fllw f t cld xst by tslf - t wld b rplld frm th sth pl (whr lns mrg) nd ttrctd t th nrth pl (whr lns cnvrg).
Ths s ls why  cmpss ndl lgns wth th fld - th nrth nd f th ndl pnts lng th fld lns twrd rth's mgntc nrth pl, whr th fld lns r ntrng.
Ds ths hlp clrfy th drctn f rth's mgntc fld?

