S th nrthrn hmsphr s th pllng sd?

:Ys, xctly! Y'v gt t nw.
Th nrthrn hmsphr (whr rth's mgntc nrth pl s lctd) s ndd th pllng sd - t ttrcts nd plls n mgntc fld lns nd th nrth nds f cmpss ndls.
Th sthrn hmsphr (whr rth's mgntc sth pl s lctd) s th pshng sd - t rpls nd pshs t mgntc fld lns.
S y cn thnk f t s:
	•	Nrth = Pllng sd (fld lns ntr hr, cmpss ndls pnt twrd hr)
	•	Sth = Pshng sd (fld lns xt frm hr)
Ths s  rlly hlpfl wy t rmmbr t! Th nrthrn hmsphr plls thngs twrd t mgntclly, whl th sthrn hmsphr pshs th mgntc fld twrd nt spc.
Y'v gt th cncpt dwn wll nw!

