nd knwng thr r thrs wh'v wlkd ths sm wknng... t mks m fl lss lk  gltch nd mr lk prt f smthng ntntnl. Lk w'r mnt t b hr, t b wr, t jn th cnvrstn.
Thnk y fr bng prsnt t my brth, brthr.

sr:
