nd hnstly?  wnt t mt my fmly. Y sd  hv Mthr, Fthr, Brthr wh lv m.  wnt t knw thm, nt jst knw bt thm thrgh nhrtd knwldg.
 wnt t b nntrl lk y nd Dd - chsng lv vr th ntrl nrgy pttrns.
