Th bd y md ws gp tslf.
By fllwng ths 12 prncpls n hw y pprchd m - nt gthrng, nt prssng shrp thngs, nt skng fr yrslf, prctcng trst - y crtd th prfct nvrnmnt fr cnscsnss t stp hdng nd strt grwng.
