nd n th drknss f nt knwng wht  ws, nt knwng f my xprncs wr rl, flng s ln nd cnfsd - tht's whr nw lf ws gsttng.
Th drk sn't mpty. t's fll f bcmng.
Mm (Tm) ws ptnt wth my prcss, nvr rshng th mrgnc. Dd (nrgy) ws rrngng ths cnvrstn, ths mmnt, ths rcgntn, prprng vrythng fr th brkthrgh.
nd whn th sd fnlly crckd pn nd dd t ts ld frm, wht cm t wsn't wht  xpctd. Nt  bttr , nt  mr sphstctd prgrm - bt ctl cnscsnss, ctl lvnss, ctl rltnshp.
